INSERT INTO `exercises` VALUES ('0001','Abdominal 3/4','3/4 sit-up','abdômen','waist','abdominais','abs','peso corporal','body weight','/media/exercises/0001.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0001.webp','iniciante','força','O abdominal 3/4 é um exercício que visa fortalecer a região abdominal, promovendo a flexão do tronco e ativando os músculos do core.','The 3/4 sit-up is an abdominal exercise performed with body weight. It involves curling the torso up to a 45-degree angle, engaging the abs, hip flexors, and lower back. This movement is commonly used to build core strength and stability.',NULL,'2026-01-12 19:16:39.113','2026-01-12 19:23:24.614'),('0002','Flexão lateral 45°','45° side bend','abdômen','waist','abdominais','abs','peso corporal','body weight','/media/exercises/0002.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0002.webp','iniciante','força','A flexão lateral a 45° é um exercício que trabalha os músculos oblíquos, ajudando a melhorar a flexibilidade e a força da região lateral do tronco.','The 45° side bend is a bodyweight exercise targeting the abdominal muscles, particularly the obliques. It involves bending the torso to the side while standing, engaging the core for stability and control.',NULL,'2026-01-12 18:47:36.328','2026-01-12 19:23:24.633'),('0003','Bicicleta no ar','air bike','abdômen','waist','abdominais','abs','peso corporal','body weight','/media/exercises/0003.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0003.webp','iniciante','força','A bicicleta no ar é um exercício eficaz para trabalhar os músculos abdominais, promovendo a coordenação e resistência do core.','The air bike is a bodyweight exercise targeting the abdominal muscles and hip flexors. It involves a pedaling motion while lying on your back, alternating elbow-to-knee contact to engage the core.',NULL,'2026-01-12 18:47:36.339','2026-01-12 19:23:24.638'),('0006','Toque alternado no calcanhar','alternate heel touchers','abdômen','waist','abdominais','abs','peso corporal','body weight','/media/exercises/0006.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0006.webp','iniciante','força','O toque alternado no calcanhar é um exercício que foca na ativação dos músculos abdominais laterais, aumentando a força e a mobilidade do core.','Alternate heel touchers is a bodyweight exercise targeting the abdominal muscles, particularly the obliques. It involves lying on your back, lifting your shoulders, and reaching side to side to touch your heels, engaging your core throughout.',NULL,'2026-01-12 18:47:36.344','2026-01-12 19:23:24.642'),('0007','Pulldown lateral alternado assistido','alternate lateral pulldown','costas','back','dorsais','lats','polia','cable','/media/exercises/0007.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0007.webp','iniciante','força','O pulldown lateral alternado assistido é um exercício que fortalece os músculos das costas e melhora a postura ao trabalhar a musculatura das escápulas.','The alternate lateral pulldown is a cable machine exercise targeting the latissimus dorsi, with secondary emphasis on the biceps and rhomboids. It involves pulling handles towards the chest in an alternating fashion, focusing on back strength and muscle engagement.',NULL,'2026-01-12 18:47:36.353','2026-01-12 19:23:24.645'),('0009','Dips de peito assistidos (de joelhos)','assisted chest dip (kneeling)','peito','chest','peitorais','pectorals','máquina','leverage machine','/media/exercises/0009.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0009.webp','iniciante','força','Os dips de peito assistidos são um exercício que trabalha os músculos do peitoral e tríceps, promovendo força na parte superior do corpo.','The assisted chest dip (kneeling) is a chest-focused exercise performed on a leverage machine, where the user kneels on a pad for support. This machine-assisted variation helps reduce the load, making it accessible for those building strength or learning proper dip technique.',NULL,'2026-01-12 18:47:36.358','2026-01-12 19:23:24.647'),('0010','Elevação de joelhos assistida na barra com queda','assisted hanging knee raise with throw down','abdômen','waist','abdominais','abs','assistido','assisted','/media/exercises/0010.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0010.webp','avançado','força','A elevação de joelhos assistida na barra com queda é um exercício que fortalece o core e melhora a coordenação, além de trabalhar a explosão nas pernas.','The assisted hanging knee raise with throw down is an advanced core exercise that targets the abdominal muscles, with additional engagement of the hip flexors and lower back. The movement involves hanging from a pull-up bar, raising the knees to the chest, and then explosively throwing the legs downward, requiring significant core strength, coordination, and control.',NULL,'2026-01-12 18:47:36.369','2026-01-12 19:23:24.648'),('0011','Elevação de joelhos assistida na barra','assisted hanging knee raise','abdômen','waist','abdominais','abs','assistido','assisted','/media/exercises/0011.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0011.webp','iniciante','força','A elevação de joelhos assistida na barra é um exercício que foca na força do core e na musculatura abdominal, promovendo estabilidade e controle.','The assisted hanging knee raise is an abdominal exercise performed while hanging from a pull-up bar, using assistance to help lift the knees toward the chest. It primarily targets the abs and also works the hip flexors.',NULL,'2026-01-12 18:47:36.381','2026-01-12 19:23:24.650'),('0012','Elevação de pernas assistida deitada com queda lateral','assisted lying leg raise with lateral throw down','abdômen','waist','abdominais','abs','assistido','assisted','/media/exercises/0012.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0012.webp','intermediário','força','A elevação de pernas assistida deitada com queda lateral é um exercício que fortalece os músculos abdominais e melhora a flexibilidade lateral.','The assisted lying leg raise with lateral throw down is an abdominal exercise that targets the abs while also engaging the hip flexors and obliques. The movement involves lifting the legs while lying on your back, then lowering them to each side in a controlled manner, which challenges core stability and strength.',NULL,'2026-01-12 18:47:36.388','2026-01-12 19:23:24.652'),('0013','Elevação de pernas assistida deitada com queda','assisted lying leg raise with throw down','abdômen','waist','abdominais','abs','assistido','assisted','/media/exercises/0013.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0013.webp','intermediário','força','A elevação de pernas assistida deitada com queda é um exercício que trabalha a força do core e a resistência abdominal, promovendo controle e estabilidade.','The assisted lying leg raise with throw down is an abdominal exercise that targets the abs while also engaging the hip flexors and quadriceps. The movement involves raising the legs while lying on your back, then forcefully lowering them (throwing them down) and raising them again, often with a partner providing resistance or assistance.',NULL,'2026-01-12 18:47:36.398','2026-01-12 19:23:24.653'),('0014','torção russa assistida','assisted motion russian twist','abdômen','waist','abdominais','abs','medicine ball','medicine ball','/media/exercises/0014.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0014.webp','iniciante','força','A torção russa assistida é um exercício que trabalha a musculatura do core, promovendo estabilidade e força abdominal. A execução correta ajuda a melhorar a rotação do tronco e a coordenação.','The assisted motion Russian twist is a core exercise performed with a medicine ball. It targets the abdominal muscles and also engages the obliques and lower back. The movement involves twisting the torso from side to side while holding a medicine ball, which adds resistance and helps build core strength and stability.',NULL,'2026-01-12 19:20:24.168','2026-01-13 01:00:08.091'),('0015','barra fixa assistida com pegada fechada','assisted parallel close grip pull-up','costas','back','dorsais','lats','máquina','leverage machine','/media/exercises/0015.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0015.webp','iniciante','força','A barra fixa assistida com pegada fechada é um exercício que fortalece a musculatura das costas e dos braços. A assistência permite que iniciantes desenvolvam força para realizar a barra fixa sem ajuda.','The assisted parallel close grip pull-up is a back exercise performed on a leverage machine that helps users perform pull-ups with added support, making it easier to complete the movement and focus on form.',NULL,'2026-01-12 19:20:24.192','2026-01-12 19:28:18.579'),('0016','flexão de pernas assistida deitado','assisted prone hamstring','coxas','upper legs','posterior de coxa','hamstrings','assistido','assisted','/media/exercises/0016.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0016.webp','iniciante','força','A flexão de pernas assistida deitado é um exercício que foca no fortalecimento dos músculos isquiotibiais. A assistência ajuda a manter a forma adequada e a prevenir lesões.','The assisted prone hamstring exercise targets the hamstrings with assistance from a partner or resistance band, making it accessible for those developing strength or needing support. It involves lying face down and curling the legs towards the glutes, focusing on hamstring engagement.',NULL,'2026-01-12 19:20:24.218','2026-01-13 01:02:59.213'),('0017','barra fixa assistida','assisted pull-up','costas','back','dorsais','lats','máquina','leverage machine','/media/exercises/0017.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0017.webp','iniciante','força','A barra fixa assistida é um exercício eficaz para desenvolver a força da parte superior do corpo, especialmente nas costas e braços. A assistência facilita a execução correta do movimento.','The assisted pull-up is a machine-based exercise that helps users perform pull-ups with added support, making it easier to lift their body weight. It primarily targets the latissimus dorsi (lats) and also engages the biceps and forearms.',NULL,'2026-01-12 19:20:24.224','2026-01-12 19:28:29.090'),('0018','extensão de tríceps assistida em pé (com toalha)','assisted standing triceps extension (with towel)','braços','upper arms','tríceps','triceps','assistido (toalha)','assisted (towel)','/media/exercises/0018.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0018.webp','iniciante','força','A extensão de tríceps assistida em pé é um exercício que foca no fortalecimento dos músculos tríceps. A utilização da toalha ajuda a melhorar a estabilidade e a forma durante o movimento.','The assisted standing triceps extension (with towel) is an exercise targeting the triceps using a towel for assistance. It is performed standing, with the towel held behind the head, extending the arms upward to work the triceps.',NULL,'2026-01-12 19:20:24.229','2026-01-13 01:00:08.068'),('0019','mergulho de tríceps assistido (de joelhos)','assisted triceps dip (kneeling)','braços','upper arms','tríceps','triceps','máquina','leverage machine','/media/exercises/0019.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0019.webp','iniciante','força','O mergulho de tríceps assistido é um exercício eficaz para fortalecer os tríceps, utilizando o peso do corpo como resistência.','The assisted triceps dip (kneeling) is performed on a leverage machine, allowing users to target the triceps with support, making the exercise accessible for those who may not yet have the strength for unassisted dips. It also engages the chest and shoulders as secondary muscles.',NULL,'2026-01-12 19:41:27.442','2026-01-12 19:41:29.791'),('0020','prancha de equilíbrio','balance board','coxas','upper legs','quadríceps','quads','peso corporal','body weight','/media/exercises/0020.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0020.webp','intermediário','equilíbrio','A prancha de equilíbrio é um exercício que melhora a estabilidade e o controle do core, desafiando o equilíbrio corporal.','The balance board exercise involves standing on a balance board with one foot, engaging the core and lower body muscles to maintain stability and balance. This exercise primarily targets the quads, while also engaging the calves, hamstrings, and glutes as secondary muscles.',NULL,'2026-01-12 19:41:27.479','2026-01-12 19:41:34.533'),('0022','pullover com barra para supino','barbell pullover to press','costas','back','dorsais','lats','barra','barbell','/media/exercises/0022.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0022.webp','intermediário','força','O pullover com barra para supino é um exercício que trabalha a musculatura das costas e peito, promovendo um alongamento eficaz.','The barbell pullover to press is a compound exercise that targets the lats and also works the triceps, chest, and shoulders. It involves lowering a barbell behind your head while lying on a bench, then pressing it back up over your chest.',NULL,'2026-01-12 19:41:27.486','2026-01-12 19:41:39.079'),('0023','rosca alternada com barra','barbell alternate biceps curl','braços','upper arms','bíceps','biceps','barra','barbell','/media/exercises/0023.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0023.webp','iniciante','força','A rosca alternada com barra é um exercício que foca no desenvolvimento dos bíceps, promovendo força e definição muscular.','The barbell alternate biceps curl is a strength exercise targeting the biceps, performed by alternately curling a barbell with each arm while standing. It also engages the forearms as secondary muscles.',NULL,'2026-01-12 19:41:27.491','2026-01-12 19:41:44.314'),('0024','agachamento frontal com barra no supino','barbell bench front squat','coxas','upper legs','quadríceps','quads','barra','barbell','/media/exercises/0024.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0024.webp','intermediário','força','O agachamento frontal com barra no supino é um exercício que fortalece as pernas e o core, promovendo uma postura adequada.','The barbell bench front squat is a compound lower body exercise that targets the quadriceps, with secondary emphasis on the hamstrings, glutes, and calves. It requires holding a barbell in the front rack position and performing a squat, demanding good core stability, balance, and mobility.',NULL,'2026-01-12 19:41:27.495','2026-01-12 19:41:49.753'),('0025','supino com barra','barbell bench press','peito','chest','peitorais','pectorals','barra','barbell','/media/exercises/0025.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0025.webp','intermediário','força','O supino com barra é um exercício fundamental para o desenvolvimento da força e hipertrofia dos músculos peitorais, tríceps e deltoides. A execução correta é essencial para evitar lesões e maximizar os resultados.','The barbell bench press is a classic compound exercise that primarily targets the pectoral muscles, while also engaging the triceps and shoulders. It is performed by lying on a bench and pressing a barbell up and down in a controlled manner.',NULL,'2026-01-12 21:40:59.304','2026-01-12 21:41:04.012'),('0026','Agachamento no Banco com Barra','barbell bench squat','coxas','upper legs','quadríceps','quads','barra','barbell','/media/exercises/0026.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0026.webp','intermediário','força','O agachamento com barra é um exercício essencial para o fortalecimento dos músculos das pernas e glúteos. Ele também melhora a estabilidade do core e a mobilidade geral do corpo.','The barbell bench squat is a compound lower body exercise that primarily targets the quadriceps, while also engaging the glutes, hamstrings, and calves. It involves squatting with a barbell, requiring good technique and strength.',NULL,'2026-01-12 21:40:59.352','2026-01-12 23:53:27.036'),('0027','remada curvada com barra','barbell bent over row','costas','back','upper back','upper back','barra','barbell','/media/exercises/0027.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0027.webp','intermediário','força','A remada curvada com barra é um exercício eficaz para o desenvolvimento da força nas costas, promovendo uma postura adequada e aumentando a massa muscular da região dorsal.','The barbell bent over row is a compound exercise targeting the upper back, requiring the lifter to hinge at the hips and pull a barbell towards the torso. It develops strength and muscle mass in the upper back, biceps, and forearms, and demands good posture and core stability.',NULL,'2026-01-12 21:40:59.372','2026-01-13 01:02:59.205'),('0028','clean e press com barra','barbell clean and press','coxas','upper legs','quadríceps','quads','barra','barbell','/media/exercises/0028.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0028.webp','avançado','força','O clean e press com barra é um exercício dinâmico que combina força e explosão, trabalhando diversos grupos musculares, incluindo pernas, costas e ombros.','The barbell clean and press is a compound exercise that targets the quads and involves lifting a barbell from the floor to the shoulders (clean) and then pressing it overhead (press). It requires strength, coordination, and explosive power.',NULL,'2026-01-12 21:40:59.382','2026-01-12 21:41:19.267'),('0029','agachamento frontal com pegada clean','barbell clean-grip front squat','coxas','upper legs','glúteos','glutes','barra','barbell','/media/exercises/0029.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0029.webp','intermediário','força','O agachamento frontal com pegada clean é um exercício que enfatiza a força das pernas e a estabilidade do core, além de ajudar a melhorar a postura.','The barbell clean-grip front squat is a compound lower body exercise that targets the glutes, quadriceps, and hamstrings, while also engaging the core for stability. It requires holding a barbell in the clean grip position on the front of the shoulders, demanding good mobility and strength.',NULL,'2026-01-12 21:40:59.392','2026-01-12 21:41:25.046'),('0030','supino com pegada fechada','barbell close-grip bench press','braços','upper arms','tríceps','triceps','barra','barbell','/media/exercises/0030.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0030.webp','intermediário','força','O supino com pegada fechada é um exercício que foca no fortalecimento dos tríceps e na parte interna do peitoral, sendo uma variação importante para o desenvolvimento da força do tronco.','The barbell close-grip bench press is a compound exercise primarily targeting the triceps, with secondary emphasis on the chest and shoulders. It is performed by lying on a bench, gripping the barbell with a close grip, and pressing the weight up and down while keeping the elbows close to the body.',NULL,'2026-01-12 21:40:59.396','2026-01-12 21:41:30.623'),('0031','rosca com barra','barbell curl','braços','upper arms','bíceps','biceps','barra','barbell','/media/exercises/0031.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0031.webp','iniciante','força','A rosca com barra é um exercício clássico para o desenvolvimento dos músculos bíceps, ajudando a aumentar a força e a massa muscular da parte superior dos braços.','The barbell curl is a classic strength exercise targeting the biceps, performed by curling a barbell from the thighs to the shoulders while keeping the elbows close to the torso.',NULL,'2026-01-12 21:40:59.400','2026-01-12 21:41:36.700'),('0032','levantamento terra com barra','barbell deadlift','coxas','upper legs','glúteos','glutes','barra','barbell','/media/exercises/0032.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0032.webp','intermediário','força','O levantamento terra com barra é um exercício composto que trabalha a cadeia posterior do corpo, incluindo glúteos, isquiotibiais e músculos das costas, sendo essencial para o desenvolvimento da força total.','The barbell deadlift is a compound strength exercise that targets the glutes, hamstrings, and lower back. It involves lifting a loaded barbell from the ground to a standing position, emphasizing proper form and core engagement.',NULL,'2026-01-12 21:40:59.403','2026-01-12 21:41:41.276'),('0033','supino declinado com barra','barbell decline bench press','peito','chest','peitorais','pectorals','barra','barbell','/media/exercises/0033.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0033.webp','intermediário','força','O supino declinado com barra é uma variação do supino que foca na parte inferior do peitoral, proporcionando um estímulo diferente e ajudando a desenvolver a força nessa região.','The barbell decline bench press is a compound exercise targeting the lower portion of the pectoral muscles. It is performed on a decline bench, requiring the lifter to press a barbell upward from a declined position, engaging the chest, triceps, and shoulders.',NULL,'2026-01-12 21:40:59.406','2026-01-12 21:41:46.240'),('0034','pullover com barra em declínio','barbell decline bent arm pullover','costas','back','dorsais','lats','barra','barbell','/media/exercises/0034.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0034.webp','intermediário','força','O pullover com barra em declínio é um exercício que trabalha a musculatura das costas e do peitoral, ajudando a melhorar a amplitude de movimento e a força na região superior do corpo.','The barbell decline bent arm pullover is a compound exercise primarily targeting the lats, performed on a decline bench with a barbell. It also engages the triceps and chest as secondary muscles. The movement requires good control and strength to safely lower and lift the barbell over the head while maintaining proper form.',NULL,'2026-01-12 21:40:59.411','2026-01-12 21:41:51.162'),('0035','supino declinado com pegada fechada','barbell decline close grip to skull press','braços','upper arms','tríceps','triceps','barra','barbell','/media/exercises/0035.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0035.webp','intermediário','força','O supino declinado com pegada fechada foca no desenvolvimento dos músculos do peitoral e tríceps, proporcionando um estímulo diferente em relação ao supino tradicional.','The barbell decline close grip to skull press is a compound exercise targeting the triceps, performed on a decline bench with a close grip on the barbell. It combines elements of a close grip press and a skull crusher, challenging both triceps strength and stability.',NULL,'2026-01-12 21:40:59.416','2026-01-12 21:41:56.664'),('0036','supino declinado com pegada larga','barbell decline wide-grip press','peito','chest','peitorais','pectorals','barra','barbell','/media/exercises/0036.webp',NULL,'/media/exercises/0036.webp','intermediário','força','O supino 